txt.en: You have become a proficient Journeyman Metalsmith! You may now use Expert Metalsmith recipes, or continue to work towards Journeyman Metalsmith mastery.\n\nAdditionally, you are now eligible to join the <rgb=#00FF00>Metalsmith's Guild</rgb>, a special reputation faction open only to Expert Metalsmiths. To join the Metalsmith's Guild, seek out a Master or Mistress of Crafting Guilds.
